    "client_msg_id": "ce15afed-dff7-420e-b12f-702b48c82b00",
    "text": "Having done some translating long ago, I can answer that question: it depends on context. You need to figure out what the role of \"English\" is in this context, and then pick one out of mainly three options:\n1. Keep \"English\"\n2. Replace by \"Chinese\"\n3. Reformulate the surrounding paragraph to convey the intended message in a different way.",
